Do’s
Use strong and unique passwords for your accounts.
Keep your social media profile clean and professional.
Check facts before sharing any post or information.
Be polite and respectful while talking to others online.
Use privacy settings to keep your personal information safe.
Don’ts
Do not share private or sensitive details online.
Do not open unknown or suspicious links.
Avoid posting rude, harmful, or inappropriate content.
Do not forward fake news or unverified information.
Avoid downloading files or apps from unsafe sources.
